_sText:
Well this is my first map I've done. Tbh I didn't wanna make a full map, so decided to edit zm_zombie_ball_v2_2 and make an extended version but tbh along the way I turned it into my own map.

Hopefully this map should be intense, fun and require teamwork to win on both sides.

Some facts.

* 80 Spawn Points. (only tested on a 32 slot server)
* No Lighting
* My First Map

People I like to thank.

*Haggard Nuggs (Ideas)
*G-Man (Helping me with hammer)
*ATIX (Cool hammer starter video tutorial)
